            "body": "Isn't this already exposed?\n{code:xml}\n<dependency>\n    <groupId>org.apache.hadoop</groupId>\n    <artifactId>hadoop-yarn-server-tests</artifactId>\n    <type>test-jar</type>\n    <scope>test</scope>\n</dependency>\n{code}\nYou have to specify the {{test-jar}} type.",
